WEBVTT

00:02.085 --> 00:04.921
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:07.757 --> 00:08.758
Are you, uh,

00:08.758 --> 00:10.510
are you going to make
a move in our lifetime?

00:10.510 --> 00:12.796
Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah...

00:12.796 --> 00:13.797
Oh, come on, Norm.

00:13.797 --> 00:15.682
Why don't you just give
up? You're finished.

00:15.682 --> 00:16.599
Well, not necessarily.

00:16.599 --> 00:18.101
He could move this piece

00:18.101 --> 00:20.103
over to here.

00:21.104 --> 00:23.106
My God, Woody, that's brilliant.

00:23.106 --> 00:26.109
You're suggesting that after
two futile interpositions,

00:26.109 --> 00:29.396
he attempt to force unobstructed
access to the eighth rank.

00:29.396 --> 00:31.231
Well, no, I'm saying he
should take your horsey

00:31.231 --> 00:33.233
with his little pointy-headed guy.

00:35.735 --> 00:37.237
No, not that one.

00:37.237 --> 00:39.122
Too late! Checkmate!

00:39.122 --> 00:39.956
(cackles)

00:39.956 --> 00:41.207
Good game, Norm.

00:41.207 --> 00:42.042
Okay, next victim.

00:42.042 --> 00:43.543
SAM: Well, what's with this

00:43.543 --> 00:45.412
obsession with chess here, huh?

00:45.412 --> 00:46.796
Oh, it's just a hobby, Sam.

00:46.796 --> 00:47.797
You know, uh, relieve the tension.

00:47.797 --> 00:50.300
Well, I got a better
way to relieve tension.

00:50.300 --> 00:52.168
Her name's Tawny. You want her number?

00:52.168 --> 00:53.970
No, thanks, Sam.

00:53.970 --> 00:56.840
I prefer something with a little
mental stimulation as well.

00:56.840 --> 00:58.341
So read to her first.

01:00.844 --> 01:02.846
No, thanks. I'll stick to chess.

01:02.846 --> 01:04.346
You know, that and fencing

01:04.346 --> 01:06.232
were my two outlets during college.

01:06.232 --> 01:07.650
Oh, boy, fencing.

