01:10.403 --> 01:11.738
Boy, that'd make me

01:11.738 --> 01:13.239
pretty tense, too.

01:15.241 --> 01:18.244
(piano plays)

01:18.244 --> 01:21.114
? Making your way in the world today ?

01:21.114 --> 01:24.117
? Takes everything you've got ?

01:24.617 --> 01:27.120
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

01:27.120 --> 01:30.623
? Sure would help a lot ?

01:30.623 --> 01:34.127
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

01:36.296 --> 01:38.298
? Sometimes you want to go ?

01:38.298 --> 01:43.803
? Where everybody knows your name ?

01:43.803 --> 01:48.308
? And they're always glad you came ?

01:48.308 --> 01:50.810
? You want to be where you can see ?

01:50.810 --> 01:53.313
? Our troubles are all the same ?

01:53.313 --> 01:58.318
